	"type": "Article",
	"name":"This Is A tEsT!",
	"content":"<p>\n\tA man befriends a bear, who acts as his protector.\n\tOne day, while the man sleeps, the bear tries to kill a fly on the man's face with a stone.\n\tThe bear kills the fly but also kills his friend.\n</p>\n<p>\n\tThis illustrates that an unwise friend can be more dangerous than an enemy.\n</p>\n"
}
